28:33.320 --> 28:34.920
He may stay like
that for a few days.

28:35.400 --> 28:36.360
Maybe longer.

28:36.480 --> 28:38.080
Dr.  Rorish said you
can take your time.

28:38.640 --> 28:40.320
Mario!  She cramps...

28:40.560 --> 28:41.680
-Who?
-The punctured vagina.

28:41.840 --> 28:43.240
We made her to the
decompression chamber.

28:43.360 --> 28:44.320
To the decompression chamber?

28:44.440 --> 28:45.640
What are you talking about?

28:45.760 --> 28:46.720
Come quickly!

28:49.680 --> 28:50.760
How is my shark victim?

28:51.040 --> 28:52.360
Stable.
I have the post-op values.

28:52.560 --> 28:53.520
Good.

28:53.760 --> 28:57.000
I do another blood count
and order 1 g of cefotetan.

29:10.360 --> 29:11.320
Oh my God.

29:11.800 --> 29:13.600
Page Campbell.
It's back to the operating room!

29:17.360 --> 29:18.320
Come on, Debbie.

29:25.640 --> 29:26.600
Charlotte, talk to me.

29:26.880 --> 29:28.880
It's not going fast enough.
I can barely intubate them.

29:29.040 --> 29:30.000
I come in.

29:30.120 --> 29:31.320
Not possible, they are
already under pressure.

29:31.440 --> 29:32.400
What do I do now?

29:32.520 --> 29:33.480
She has to get rid of the air.

29:33.880 --> 29:36.400
I need a scalpel
and some betadine.

29:45.800 --> 29:46.760
And now?

29:46.880 --> 29:49.760
An incision in the
subcutaneous tissue of the neck.

29:58.040 --> 29:59.000
It's not working.

29:59.560 --> 30:00.720
Not so timid, Charlotte.

30:00.920 --> 30:03.160
Cut deeper, through the dermis.

30:05.200 --> 30:06.160
You can do it.

30:31.560 --> 30:33.960
It was horrible today
on the beach in Malibu.

30:34.080 --> 30:36.240
A great white shark
about four and a

30:36.400 --> 30:39.280
half meters in size
attacked three surfers.

30:39.920 --> 30:41.680
One of them was immediately
pronounced dead, and two

30:41.800 --> 30:44.960
more were flown to the
Angels Memorial by helicopter.

30:45.160 --> 30:48.800
We have just received
the report that a survivor

30:48.960 --> 30:51.200
unfortunately
succumbed to his injuries.

30:51.800 --> 30:54.600
The hospital does not
publish the victim's name yet,

30:54.760 --> 30:57.160
but we were told that he
died during the operation,

30:57.320 --> 30:58.800
which should close
his great wounds.

30:58.920 --> 30:59.880
Is that correct?

31:01.200 --> 31:02.160
Is he dead?

31:23.480 --> 31:24.440
I'm sorry Jaydin.

31:24.920 --> 31:26.760
And I'm sorry you
found out that way.

31:28.640 --> 31:29.600
He was all alone.

31:31.480 --> 31:34.040
I should have been with him.
I should have been there.

31:36.520 --> 31:37.480
I want to see him.

31:37.960 --> 31:38.920
Will you take me to him?

31:39.120 --> 31:40.080
I can not do that.

31:44.120 --> 31:45.880
First his parents
have to be there.

31:46.240 --> 31:47.320
They're on the plane!

31:48.640 --> 31:50.480
What should i do?
Just sit around?

31:52.960 --> 31:53.920
Does Kaya know?

31:54.080 --> 31:55.040
No.

31:57.360 --> 31:58.320
She mustn't do that either.

31:59.560 --> 32:00.520
Not yet.

32:01.520 --> 32:05.560
She lost 120 stitches
and a lot of blood.

32:06.760 --> 32:08.720
She has to stay calm now.

32:10.440 --> 32:11.400
This will break your heart.

32:13.200 --> 32:16.280
With the pain you're
feeling right now Jaydin

32:18.120 --> 32:19.280
you mustn't tell her.

32:21.160 --> 32:22.120
Not yet.

32:23.920 --> 32:25.760
You have to be strong for her.

32:29.040 --> 32:30.480
Who is strong for me?

32:51.680 --> 32:52.640
I do not apologize.

32:55.600 --> 32:57.120
If that's why you're here,
you can go right away.

32:58.680 --> 32:59.640
Oh yes?

33:00.800 --> 33:01.840
You do not talk to me anymore?

33:03.560 --> 33:05.120
And you want to be the
more mature of the two of us?

33:07.680 --> 33:08.640
Well, Jaydin,

33:10.240 --> 33:11.200
be a baby

33:13.560 --> 33:14.840
I'll let you rest a little.

33:18.720 --> 33:19.680
Stop!

33:21.280 --> 33:22.560
He's dead, right?

33:32.360 --> 33:33.320
Kaya...

33:33.680 --> 33:35.200
-Just go!
-Kaya, I'm so sorry...

33:35.360 --> 33:36.320
Just leave me alone

33:36.760 --> 33:38.120
You're welcome.  I'm so sorry.

33:38.560 --> 33:39.520
Please just go.

33:51.040 --> 33:52.000
Will he die?

33:53.280 --> 33:56.080
He lost a lot of blood.
He's in bad shape.

33:56.920 --> 33:57.880
Doc,

33:59.040 --> 34:00.600
will my father die?

34:02.840 --> 34:03.800
I am an optimist.

34:05.360 --> 34:06.320
Me too.

34:21.000 --> 34:21.960
Hey pop

34:24.639 --> 34:25.600
It's a nice suit.

34:28.639 --> 34:29.600
I saw him.

34:31.280 --> 34:32.560
I saw that too.

34:34.360 --> 34:35.639
You wrote a toast?

34:36.400 --> 34:38.000
You hate having to
talk in front of others.

34:39.880 --> 34:41.080
Good thing you were
spared that, wasn't it?

34:56.679 --> 34:57.640
"Randall,

35:00.120 --> 35:01.800
I remember when
you were a little boy

35:02.240 --> 35:04.200
You followed me everywhere.

35:04.520 --> 35:05.720
You needed me for everything

35:06.200 --> 35:08.560
It drove me
crazy, but I loved it.

35:10.800 --> 35:11.760
You were my boy

35:13.600 --> 35:14.920
and i loved being your dad.

35:17.400 --> 35:19.440
But it's been a long time
since you needed me

35:21.080 --> 35:24.360
It's long since you said
you wanted to be like me.

35:27.680 --> 35:30.240
Now I want to be like
you when I grow up. "

35:40.640 --> 35:42.200
I still need you.

35:43.000 --> 35:43.960
Do you hear me?

35:46.840 --> 35:48.840
I am your boy
And I still need you

36:02.440 --> 36:03.400
Kaya.

36:07.280 --> 36:08.240
Kaya.

36:11.720 --> 36:14.040
I know it is impossible
for you to understand...

36:14.320 --> 36:15.640
They think i'm still little

36:17.880 --> 36:19.240
and that I can't
understand anything.

36:21.840 --> 36:22.880
I think you are grieving

36:24.680 --> 36:27.000
Nobody understands
grief at any age.

36:29.720 --> 36:30.920
I don't want him to be gone.

36:32.720 --> 36:34.120
-He should come back.
-I know.

36:35.320 --> 36:37.280
And as bad as that is

36:38.560 --> 36:40.480
you're not the only one
who has to endure this.

36:42.120 --> 36:44.360
Jaydin doesn't understand
any better than you

36:44.520 --> 36:46.440
do, and her heart is
broken just like yours.

36:47.880 --> 36:49.240
But she thinks
it's all about her.

36:50.160 --> 36:51.480
She doesn't understand
what I'm feeling.

36:52.840 --> 36:53.800
She is your sister

36:54.600 --> 36:56.320
She's the only one who
understands what you're feeling.

37:03.640 --> 37:04.600
Talk to her.

37:05.080 --> 37:06.040
OK?

37:06.680 --> 37:08.480
This is the only way
you can both manage it.

37:10.920 --> 37:12.520
And I wouldn't
tell you any of this

37:13.120 --> 37:14.440
if i think you're too small

38:02.600 --> 38:03.560
Jaydin...

38:28.480 --> 38:29.440
I love you.

38:30.280 --> 38:31.240
I also you.

38:43.560 --> 38:44.920
The crepitation is gone.

38:48.120 --> 38:49.520
Subcutaneous emphysema?

38:51.080 --> 38:52.040
Who found out?

38:54.400 --> 38:56.160
Noa.  With Dr.  Savetti's help.

39:00.960 --> 39:01.920
Good work.

39:03.000 --> 39:03.960
From all of you.

39:04.880 --> 39:06.920
Savetti, we document that

39:07.240 --> 39:09.280
and they both get a
well-deserved break.

39:15.320 --> 39:16.280
What was that supposed to mean?

39:16.600 --> 39:17.560
I need a girlfriend.

39:18.440 --> 39:19.600
And I think you do too.

39:20.120 --> 39:21.080
Or?

39:23.200 --> 39:24.320
You didn't realize
that, did you?

39:24.880 --> 39:25.840
I was distracted.

39:26.160 --> 39:27.240
I left her alone.

39:27.640 --> 39:28.600
Sorry

39:28.880 --> 39:30.200
The second year is difficult.

39:30.680 --> 39:32.920
You are no longer solely
responsible for yourself.

39:33.200 --> 39:34.960
If you look after new ones,

39:35.120 --> 39:36.640
you are responsible for them.

39:55.880 --> 39:56.840
This is not your fault.

40:03.960 --> 40:05.560
-Sorry I said that.
-You had every right.

40:05.920 --> 40:06.880
No I did not.

40:07.800 --> 40:08.760
You did the right thing.

40:09.480 --> 40:11.720
Sometimes that doesn't
excuse us from the result.

40:12.840 --> 40:16.240
We haven't officially
introduced ourselves yet.

40:19.080 --> 40:20.040
I am angus.

40:20.240 --> 40:21.200
Ethane.

40:26.640 --> 40:28.600
We get one from
your unit every year.

40:30.080 --> 40:32.560
Either they come here as
punishment for making mistakes

40:33.120 --> 40:35.120
or because they did something good.

40:37.880 --> 40:38.840
What applies to you?

40:41.080 --> 40:42.040
Both.
